item.title: 2019 Monthly Fishing Comps
item.description: 2019 Fishing competition each month collective prizes up to $200.00 February 1-3: Barramundi 700mm challenge March 1-3: Five Species estuary Apr 5-7: Mono 3kg challenge biggest fish May 4-6: NQ Championship June 7-9: Ten Species challenge July: Club trip going away to be advised August 9-11: Coral trout 600mm challenge September 6-8: Pelagic challenge biggest fish October: Barra Bonanza Nov 15-17: Flathead Dec 13-15: Nannygai biggest fish Fishing starts Friday @ 1800 hrs ends Sunday 1500 hrs, weight in @ 1600hrs at the club house
